## Original Work

The original Dutch text *Antirevolutionaire Staatkunde* (1916–1917) by Abraham Kuyper is in the public domain. Kuyper died in 1920, placing the original work beyond copyright in most jurisdictions.

## This Translation

This English translation is an open, community-driven project. The translation text, indices, companion materials, build scripts, and all project files are released under the MIT License. You are free to use, modify, distribute, and build upon this translation for any purpose — personal, academic, commercial, or otherwise. Attribution is appreciated but not required.

## AI Disclosure

This translation was prepared with the assistance of advanced Artificial Intelligence systems. The translation is human-guided and verified. AI was used for text extraction, initial translation drafts, index synthesis, parallel text alignment, and scholarly apparatus generation.
